703122f-a.title: Brooklyn: Bay 11th Street - Cropsey Avenue
703122f-a.folder: Bay 11th Street & Cropsey Avenue, Brooklyn, NY

703889f-b.title: Brooklyn: Cropsey Avenue - Bay 11th Street
703889f-b.text:
Cropsey Ave., south side, opposite Bay 11th Street, showing the
Benmnett homestead, also known as the Cortelyou house. In 1916 it
was accuired by the Millrose Athletic Association for its Country
home. Bay 11th Street, terminated at Cropsey Ave. in 1923; hovever
the City has condemned this house, and is to continue Bay 11th Street
to Warehouse Ave., an Gwavesend Bay.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
